text: Dzhenko Sabev was a equestrian from Bulgaria. Sabev competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics. He was born on 2 June 1947 and died on 30 April 2020.Dzhenko Sabev == References == == Other websites == * Category:1947 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Event riders Category:Olympians for Bulgaria Category:Olympic equestrians
